'''斯科蒂·詹姆斯'''（{{lang-en|Scotty James}}，{{bd|1994年|7月6日||}}）生于维多利亚州墨尔本，是一名澳大利亚男子单板滑雪运动员，主攻半管项目<ref>{{cite web|title=Scotty James|url=http://sochi2014.olympics.com.au/athlete/scotty-james|work=[[澳大利亚奥林匹克委员会|Australian Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2014-02-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310213821/http://sochi2014.olympics.com.au/athlete/scotty-james|archivedate=2014-03-10}}</ref>。他在1岁时开始接触滑雪，3岁时开始接触单板滑雪，6岁时开始参加比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/snowboard/athlete-profile-n3015540-scotty-james.htm|title=Snowboard {{!}} Athlete Profile: Scotty JAMES|work=Pyeongchang 2018|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421135921/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/snowboard/athlete-profile-n3015540-scotty-james.htm|archivedate=2018-04-21}}</ref>。詹姆斯原本无缘[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年温哥华冬奥]]名单，后来由于原本入选名单的Nate Johnstone因伤放弃资格，詹姆斯便赶往[[加拿大|加拿大]]参加世界杯分站赛，最终他成功获得足够的奥运积分，并入选名单，成为该届冬奥年龄最小的男选手的同时也成为50年来年龄最小的澳大利亚男子奥运选手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,26714250-10389,00.html|title=Britteny Cox and Scott James prove size is no barrier at Winter Olympics|publisher=[[悉尼先驱晨报|Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2010-02-13|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100216132232/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,26714250-10389,00.html|archivedate=2010-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/more-sports/scotty-james-made-history-in-vancouver-now-he-has-a-new-trick-up-his-sleeve/news-story/a4420d85087efd695f24adc9b2bd0f68|title=Scotty James made history in Vancouver, now he has a new trick up his sleeve|publisher=Herald Sun|date=2014-01-12|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428005339/https://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/more-sports/scotty-james-made-history-in-vancouver-now-he-has-a-new-trick-up-his-sleeve/news-story/a4420d85087efd695f24adc9b2bd0f68|archivedate=2017-04-28}}</ref>。

